=head1 DESCRIPTION

The settings for what common media server data (CMSD) headers AWS
Elemental MediaPackage includes in responses to the CDN.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 PublishMQCS => Bool

When true, AWS Elemental MediaPackage includes the MQCS in responses to
the CDN. This setting is valid only when C<InputType> is C<CMAF>.



